            {
              "id": "JS-AUDIT-024",
              "name": "IDOR + free-deluxe upgrade in /rest/deluxe-membership",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "IDOR + free-deluxe upgrade in /rest/deluxe-membership"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Body-supplied UserId + the paymentMode branch only checks card/wallet if those modes are *named*. Omitting paymentMode skips payment entirely and still promotes the chosen UserId to 'deluxe', as the route's freeDeluxeChallenge helper confirms."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Recommended fix: Authoritative UserId from JWT; require a payment mode; transactionally debit + upgrade.",
                "markdown": "## IDOR + free-deluxe upgrade in /rest/deluxe-membership\n\n**CWE:** CWE-639\n\n**OWASP:** A01:2021-Broken Access Control\n\n### Exploitation\n\nBody-supplied UserId + the paymentMode branch only checks card/wallet if those modes are *named*. Omitting paymentMode skips payment entirely and still promotes the chosen UserId to 'deluxe', as the route's freeDeluxeChallenge helper confirms.\n\n### Recommended Fix\n\nAuthoritative UserId from JWT; require a payment mode; transactionally debit + upgrade."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
