            {
              "id": "JS-AUDIT-028",
              "name": "Sequelize where-injection via JSON.parse(req.params.id) in /api/Recycles/:id",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Sequelize where-injection via JSON.parse(req.params.id) in /api/Recycles/:id"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Parsing `req.params.id` as JSON lets an attacker pass `{\"$gt\":0}` or other Sequelize operator objects into the where clause, dumping the entire Recycles table. Throws on bad input, but valid JSON objects/operators are accepted directly."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Recommended fix: Coerce id to Number; do not JSON.parse user path parameters.",
                "markdown": "## Sequelize where-injection via JSON.parse(req.params.id) in /api/Recycles/:id\n\n**CWE:** CWE-89\n\n**OWASP:** A03:2021-Injection\n\n### Exploitation\n\nParsing `req.params.id` as JSON lets an attacker pass `{\"$gt\":0}` or other Sequelize operator objects into the where clause, dumping the entire Recycles table. Throws on bad input, but valid JSON objects/operators are accepted directly.\n\n### Recommended Fix\n\nCoerce id to Number; do not JSON.parse user path parameters."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "error"
              },
              "properties": {
                "security-severity": "7.4",
                "tags": [
                  "sql_injection",
                  "tier3"
                ],
                "precision": "high",
                "cwe": [
                  "CWE-89"
                ],
                "owasp": [
                  "A03:2021-Injection"
                ],
                "triage": "confirmed"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "JS-AUDIT-029",
              "name": "Chatbot remote training data download + dynamic dispatch on botUtils[handler]",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Chatbot remote training data download + dynamic dispatch on botUtils[handler]"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "If `application.chatBot.trainingData` is configured to a URL, the server fetches *unauthenticated* code-influencing data over the network with no integrity check (no checksum/signature). Anyone able to MITM or compromise the host serving the training data can change bot intents — including ones that influence the `handler` dispatch through botUtils. CodeQL flags the property-injection pattern (alerts 50-54)."
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "Recommended fix: Pin and SHA-256 verify training assets; load from a trusted, immutable URL or repository; whitelist `response.handler` against a constant map.",
                "markdown": "## Chatbot remote training data download + dynamic dispatch on botUtils[handler]\n\n**CWE:** CWE-94\n\n**OWASP:** A08:2021-Software and Data Integrity Failures\n\n### Exploitation\n\nIf `application.chatBot.trainingData` is configured to a URL, the server fetches *unauthenticated* code-influencing data over the network with no integrity check (no checksum/signature). Anyone able to MITM or compromise the host serving the training data can change bot intents — including ones that influence the `handler` dispatch through botUtils. CodeQL flags the property-injection pattern (alerts 50-54).\n\n### Recommended Fix\n\nPin and SHA-256 verify training assets; load from a trusted, immutable URL or repository; whitelist `response.handler` against a constant map."
              },
              "defaultConfiguration": {
                "level": "error"
              },
              "properties": {
                "security-severity": "7.2",
                "tags": [
                  "supply_chain",
                  "remote_property_injection",
                  "tier3"
                ],
                "precision": "medium",
                "cwe": [
                  "CWE-94"
                ],
                "owasp": [
                  "A08:2021-Software and Data Integrity Failures"
                ],
                "triage": "confirmed"
              }
            },
