                "text": "Prometheus metrics include process metrics (memory, CPU, event-loop lag), request counts/labels (revealing endpoints), and a custom file-upload histogram. Useful for an attacker mapping the API surface and confirming successful exploitation (e.g. when memory spikes on yaml-bomb)."
