          "ruleId": "JS-AUDIT-001",
          "level": "error",
          "message": {
            "text": "POST /rest/user/login passes req.body.email directly into a raw template literal SQL query. Sending email='\\' OR 1=1--' is a textbook tautology bypass that returns the first row (the admin) and the route then issues a JWT for that user via security.authorize(). No parameterization, no escaping, no allow-list. The result is full admin takeover from an entirely unauthenticated request."
          },
