            "text": "GET /rest/products/search?q= is reachable without authentication and concatenates the query parameter directly into raw SQL. Because the database is SQLite the attacker can append a UNION SELECT statement to exfiltrate Users (emails, MD5 password hashes) and sqlite_master (table schemas). The route code itself solves a 'unionSqlInjectionChallenge' by detecting if user rows leak via this primitive, which proves it is exploitable end-to-end."
          },
